---
// src/components/Footer.astro
// No necesitamos importar nada ya que usaremos HTML/Astro estándar
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="w-full bg-zinc-900 text-gray-300 border-t-4 border-[#f0ba18]">
    
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 lg:gap-8">

            <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left space-y-6">
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <h3 class="font-brand text-2xl text-white uppercase tracking-wider">
                        Grupo <span class="text-[#f0ba18]">Transportes RG</span>
                    </h3>
                    <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-[#f0ba18] rounded-full mx-auto md:mx-0"></div>
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400">
                    Somos tu aliado estratégico en logística y mudanzas. Conectamos destinos con seguridad, cumplimiento y la confianza que mereces.
                </p>

                <a href="https://wa.me/573225019305" target="_blank"
                   class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#f0ba18] hover:bg-white text-black font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
                    <i class="fab fa-whatsapp text-xl"></i>
                    <span>¡Cotiza Ahora!</span>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left">
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-6 uppercase tracking-wide border-b-2 border-[#f0ba18] pb-2 inline-block">
                    Navegación
                </h4>
                <ul class="space-y-3 w-full">
                    <li>
                        <a href="/" class="group flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2 hover:text-[#f0ba18] transition-colors">
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-xs text-[#f0ba18] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></i>
                            Inicio
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/servicios" class="group flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2 hover:text-[#f0ba18] transition-colors">
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-xs text-[#f0ba18] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></i>
                            Servicios
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/nosotros" class="group flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2 hover:text-[#f0ba18] transition-colors">
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-xs text-[#f0ba18] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></i>
                            Nosotros
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/contacto" class="group flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2 hover:text-[#f0ba18] transition-colors">
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-xs text-[#f0ba18] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></i>
                            Contacto
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left">
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-6 uppercase tracking-wide border-b-2 border-[#f0ba18] pb-2 inline-block">
                    Legal
                </h4>
                <ul class="space-y-3 w-full">
                    <li>
                        <a href="#" class="hover:text-[#f0ba18] transition-colors">Política de Datos</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#" class="hover:text-[#f0ba18] transition-colors">Términos y Condiciones</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#" class="hover:text-[#f0ba18] transition-colors">Preguntas Frecuentes</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left">
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-6 uppercase tracking-wide border-b-2 border-[#f0ba18] pb-2 inline-block">
                    Contáctanos
                </h4>
                <ul class="space-y-4 w-full text-sm">
                    <li class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#f0ba18]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-[#f0ba18]">
                            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Sede Principal:</strong>
                            <span class="block">La Virginia, Risaralda</span>
                            <span class="block">Calle 16A #4A - 05</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-3">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#f0ba18]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-[#f0ba18]">
                            <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Llámanos:</strong>
                            <a href="tel:+573207797441" class="hover:text-[#f0ba18] transition-colors">320 779 7441</a>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="pt-2">
                        <a href="#" class="text-[#f0ba18] text-xs uppercase font-bold hover:text-white transition-colors border-b border-[#f0ba18] hover:border-white pb-0.5">
                            Ver ubicación en mapa
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-black py-6 border-t border-zinc-800">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-xs text-gray-500">
            <p>
                © {currentYear} <span class="text-[#f0ba18] font-bold">Grupo Transportes RG</span>. Todos los derechos reservados.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f text-lg"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors"><i class="fab fa-instagram text-lg"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors"><i class="fab fa-whatsapp text-lg"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</footer>